Mario asked you to build him a website that keeps track of how many 
baddies he caught for Princess Peach so he can send her a bill.
Extra Credit
Build Mario Pest Control website to be responsive,
meaning it looks great when shrunk down to the screen size of a smart phone.

Pricing: X

Goombas: 5 Coins X
Bob-ombs: 7 Coins X
Cheep-cheeps: 11 Coins X
Baddies Caught:

The number of baddies caught will be entered into thier input fields. 
Each baddies type will have their own input feild.

Total Price

This will be dynamic depending on how many baddies were caught.

Project Requirements
The website must contain the following:
1.
A list displaying each baddie by type. Each list item must:
Have baddie image X
Have baddie name X
Show price of that baddie X
Have an input box to enter the total caught of that type X
A total price at the bottom that sums the total cost of baddies caught /
(must use Javascript for this math - no hard coded values)

2.
A footer showing:
Mario's email address X
Mario's company website url X
Mario's physical address X
A large title at the top of the page entitled "Mario Pest Control" X
Passing Criteria: Visual Inspection by Instructor
Student demonstrated a solid understanding with the following levels of the skills tree:

Static Websites, Level 1
CSS Selectors
Colors in CSS
Fonts in CSS
Using external CSS stylesheets and JavaScript files
Deployment, Level 1
Opening an HTML document in browser
